    <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>Welcome to ShareSmallBiz!</p>

    <p>This privacy policy explains how ShareSmallBiz.com ("we", "our", "us") collects, uses, and protects any information that you give us when you use this website.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">Data Collection</h2>
    <p>We are committed to ensuring that your privacy is protected. As part of our platform, we collect and process user registration information and user-created content. Additionally, we may moderate user-generated content in the future to ensure compliance with our community guidelines and platform policies.</p>
