    <p>ShareSmallBiz.com is currently under development, and new features and functionalities may be introduced over time. As the platform evolves, this privacy policy and our terms and conditions will be updated accordingly. We encourage users to review this page periodically to stay informed about how their information is being managed.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>ShareSmallBiz.com may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page. You are advised to review this privacy policy periodically for any changes.</p>

